curity or Information Technology or five or more yearsequivalent work experience as a security analyst- Five or more years hands-on working experience with Check Point, Cisco,Juniper, Palo Alto Networks firewalls and unified threat managementarchitectur- Relevant Information Security Certifications (CISSP, CISM, CISA,CCNP, CCSP, GIAC, ACE, etc.) strongly desired- Working knowledge of well-known networking protocols and services(TCP/IP, LDAP, Radius, IPX, NETBUI, IPSEC, HTTPS, SSL,SSH, SFTP, SMTP, PPTP, PPP, SMB, SNMP, RIP, Windows, UNIX, Linux)- Hand-on experience managing IP Networks, Intrusion Detection Sensors(host and network), Intrusion Prevention Systems and firewalls highly desired- Excellent oral and written communication skills- Ability to read and interpret documents such as network drawings, systemsprints, operating instructions and procedure manuals- Excellent analytical and problem solving skills- Works well in a team environment and independently- Excellent interpersonal and organizational skills- Strong customer service attitudeEEO EmployerApex Systems LLC is an Equal Opportunity/Affirmative Action Employer.</p><p>Weevaluate qualified applicants without regard to race, color, religion,sex, national origin, disability, veteran status, and other protectedcharacteristics.</p><p>If you have visited our website in search of information onemployment opportunities or to apply for a position, and you require anaccommodation in using our website for a search or application, pleasecontact our Employee Services Department at .EEO EmployerApex Systems LLC is an Equal Opportunity/Affirmative Action Employer.</p><p>Weevaluate qualified applicants without regard to race, color, religion,sex, national origin, disability, veteran status, and other protectedcharacteristics.</p><p>If you have visited our website in search of information onemployment opportunities or to apply for a position, and you require anaccommodation in using our website for a search or application